{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":7,"day":23}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"高唱凯歌向未来","authors":["张红曙/李存葆"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天生辉呵云结彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜庆的锣鼓擂起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌如潮呵情满怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝捷的鞭炮点起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼党中央英明决定；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱党的十届三中全会胜利召开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，英明领袖华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神彩奕奕多豪迈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是毛主席的好学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是我们的好统帅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席和人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最知人民恨和爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席继承毛主席遗志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举为民除“四害”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，敬爱的叶副主席不老松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辅佐领袖斩狼豺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命再长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军的传统传后代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我们的邓副主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四人帮”对您打击又陷害。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪辱霜欺无所惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春回大地凯旋来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王张江姚“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个反革命的极右派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日呵，党把“四害”清除掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿神州齐称快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天生辉呵云结彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席伟大旗帜举起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧跟英明领袖华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高唱凯歌向未来！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}